- 🔌 [computer-use-linux](https://github.com/avifenesh/computer-use-linux) — Linux desktop-control MCP server for Rayovin and other MCP hosts, with AT-SPI accessibility trees, Wayland/X11 input, screenshots, and compositor window targeting.
- 🔌 [RayovinClaw](https://github.com/AaronWong1999/rayovinclaw) — Community WeChat bridge: Run Rayovin Agent and OpenClaw on the same WeChat account.

